<h2>Reviews: The Trust Signal That Drives Rankings</h2>
<p>Reviews are both a ranking factor and a conversion factor. <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey/">97% of consumers read reviews before choosing a local business</a>. Google uses review count, rating quality, and recency as direct ranking signals.</p>
